        <p style="font-size:1.12rem;color:var(--ink-2);max-width:560px">WLP-1 is the daily oral GLP-1 support formula built on three clinically studied actives shown to <strong>boost natural GLP-1 by up to 321%</strong>, quiet food noise, and help users lose an average of <strong>~9 lbs in 4 weeks</strong>, naturally.</p>
